'''天劍局'''（{{lang-en|'''S.W.O.R.D.'''}}），正式名稱為'''知性世界觀測與應對局'''（{{lang|en|'''S'''entient '''W'''orld '''O'''bservation and '''R'''esponse '''D'''epartment}}），是[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]中一個科幻的[[反恐|反恐]]組織兼情報機構，其宗旨是應對地外威脅。<ref name="CHICAGO CON '09: S.W.O.R.D. ONGOING">{{Cite web |url =http://marvel.com/news/comics/2009/8/10/9122/chicago_con_09_sword_ongoing |title =CHICAGO CON '09: S.W.O.R.D. ONGOING |author =Marc Strom |date =2009-08-10 |publisher =Marvel.com |language =en |accessdate =2014-08-06 |format = |quote = |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140502110151/http://marvel.com/news/comics/2009/8/10/9122/chicago_con_09_sword_ongoing |archivedate =2014-05-02 |dead-url =no }}</ref><ref name="title =S.W.O.R.D.: THE CUTTING EDGE">{{Cite web|url =http://marvel.com/news/comics/2009/10/12/9882/sword_the_cutting_edge|title =S.W.O.R.D.: THE CUTTING EDGE|author =Jim Beard|date =2009-10-12|publisher =Marvel.com|language =en|accessdate =2014-08-06|format =|quote =|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140404181814/http://marvel.com/news/comics/2009/10/12/9882/sword_the_cutting_edge|archivedate =2014-04-04|dead-url =no}}</ref>
該組織最早登場於2004年開始連載的《Astonishing X-Men》。
著名成員包括[[X戰警|X戰警]]的[[野獸_(漫畫)|野獸]]與{{link-en|洛克希德 (漫畫)|Lockheed (comics)|洛克希德}}、復仇者的[[女蜘蛛人_(潔西卡·德魯)|女蜘蛛人]]以及特工{{link-en|艾比蓋爾·布蘭德|Abigail Brand}}與{{link-en|亨利·彼得·傑瑞奇|Henry Peter Gyrich}}。

